snippet.title: Warhammer Combat Cards Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Build a powerful army of cards from your favourite faction in the Warhammer 40,000 universe and battle other players in fast-paced, turn based online combat! In the grim darkness of the far future there is only war!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1641990
Publsiher: The Phoenix Lighthouse GmbH
Developer: Well Played Games
